            "name": "Clouded Charge",
            "subtype": "ability",
            "text": "The mist bear Strides twice. During this movement, wisps of ethereal smoke trail from its body, making it concealed. The mist bear then Strikes. The target is off-guard to this attack if the bear moved at least 20 feet.",
